          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>
                                        <date>Sept 15<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1853</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>Dear Friend,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">I have waited <sic>untill</sic> I had<lb/> heard
                                        of <persName>Rehines</persName> safety, ere I wrote for
                                        the<lb/> books, he has left <placeName>New
                                                  Orleans</placeName>, at length, and<lb/> is
                                        staying with <persName>Sarah Levy</persName>, at the
                                                  “<placeName>Bay of St Louis</placeName>”<lb/>
                                        thanks be to God, my children, have been spared<lb/> the
                                        dreadful scourge. You did not see
                                                  <persName>Rosalie</persName><lb/> I suppose as
                                        they must have passed through<lb/> immediately, since the
                                        arrived in <placeName>Baltimore</placeName><lb/> the same
                                        evening they left; here; imagine my delight<lb/> at her
                                        unexpected visit altho' of short duration.<lb/>
                                        <persName>Augusts Block</persName>, is still here, perhaps
                                        you could<lb/> send the Books with his, or by some
                                        opportunity<lb/> before the holy days—I will only take one
                                                  <hi rend="underline">set</hi><lb/> of the smallest
                                        size and cheapest for <persName>Herman's</persName> use<lb/>
                                        if you recollect the two last <hi rend="underline"
                                                  >daily</hi> you sent me<lb/> I'd like them to
                                        match as nearly as possible<lb/> I shall be obliged to have
                                        a daily with the<lb/>
                                        <hi rend="underline">set</hi> as I gave one of the others to
                                                  <persName>Esther</persName>: you'll<lb/> charge
                                        them with Bible to <persName>Rehine</persName>—</p>
                              <p>When I can afford it I will have all “<persName>Grace<lb/>
                                                  Aguillars</persName> works” at present must be
                                        satisfied<lb/> when I wrote you there was a prospect of
                                        better<lb/> times, which has since taken flight—<persName>Mr
                                                  Moses Jacob</persName>,<lb/> I mean, has a Son
                                        named to day a very fine<lb/> affair I'm told, <persName>Mrs
                                                  Ottilingua</persName> is here.—</p>
                              <p>Please mention me to my <persName>Aunt Grace</persName>, I wish</p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>I could see her here for the holy days, say to<lb/>
                                        <persName role="author">Abby</persName> new house, when I
                                        write her again, I<lb/> shall get an answer I hope, also
                                        remember me<lb/> to <persName>Mrs Florence</persName>, and
                                                  <persName>Miriam Spatts</persName>—<lb/> hope to
                                        see you soon remain as ever</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">your true friend</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">
                                        <persName role="author">Abby Block</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>if an enquire of me give my<lb/> respects—Aunty is as usual.<lb/>
                                        please when you write again<lb/> let it be more <hi
                                                  rend="underline">distinct</hi> I am<lb/> getting
                                                  <hi rend="underline">old</hi>—</p>
                              <pb n="3"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <hi rend="underline">Paid</hi>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <hi rend="underline">To</hi>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)"><addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)"><placeName><hi rend="underline"
                                                  >Philadelphia</hi></placeName>.</p>
